  hook:"Apple Vision Pro projects 23 million pixels across your field of vision — more than a 4K TV per eye — while tracking your hands, eyes, and body in real-time. Meta Quest 3 lets you play tennis in your living room against a virtual opponent superimposed on your real furniture. India's AR/VR market is projected to reach ₹14,000 crore by 2027, with applications from ISRO training astronauts in virtual spacewalks to Reliance Jio building immersive cricket experiences. AR overlays digital information on the real world (Pokémon GO, Instagram filters, Google Maps AR navigation). VR replaces the real world entirely with a computer-generated one (gaming, training, virtual tourism). How do headsets trick your brain into believing digital worlds are real?",
